headline: Travelers Publishes Its 2024 Sustainability Report
summary: HARTFORD, Conn., June 26, 2025--The Travelers Companies, Inc. (NYSE: TRV) today announced the release of its 2024 Sustainability Report, which details the company’s integrated approach to sustained value creation.
